This is a Python/Electron trading copilot project deployed on Railway.

PROJECT STRUCTURE:
- backend/ → All Python scripts
- data/ → JSON data files (created at runtime)
- config/keys.env → API keys
- index.html → Electron GUI
- main.js → Electron entry point

KEY FILES:
- backend/master_analyzer.py → Main AI analysis engine (v9)
- backend/master_scheduler.py → Schedules all jobs with IST timezone
- backend/ai_router.py → Routes between Gemini/Claude/Haiku
- backend/telegram_brain_pusher.py → Sends alerts to Telegram
- backend/telegram_listener.py → Handles Telegram bot commands
- backend/api/api_server.py → FastAPI server on Railway (uvicorn entry)
- backend/collector.py → Fetches NSE stock prices
- backend/stock_scanner.py → Scans NSE 500 for signals
- backend/prediction_logger.py → Logs AI predictions to SQLite
- backend/outcome_tracker.py → Evaluates WIN/LOSS daily at 8am
- backend/learning_engine.py → RAG calibration from past performance
- backend/reddit_tracker.py → Reddit sentiment (uses old.reddit.com RSS)
- backend/govt_tracker.py → Govt/SEBI/BSE RSS feeds
- backend/youtube_tracker.py → YouTube TV channel tracking
- backend/telegram_scraper.py → Telegram channel scraping (optional)

CRITICAL RULES:
1. NEVER use "from core.builders" - that module does not exist
2. NEVER use "from core." anything - core/ directory does not exist
3. Data directory: Path(__file__).parent.parent / 'data'
4. Config: Path(__file__).parent.parent / 'config' / 'keys.env'
5. Always use IST timezone (pytz Asia/Kolkata) for scheduling
6. Model names must be exact:
   - claude-sonnet-4-5 (NOT claude-sonnet-4-5-20241022)
   - claude-haiku-3-5-20241022 (NOT claude-haiku-4-5)
   - gemini-2.0-flash (NOT gemini-1.5-flash)
7. Railway volume auto-mounts to the data directory
8. All scripts must handle None returns gracefully
9. Reddit: use old.reddit.com RSS feeds (JSON API returns 403)
10. Telegram scraper: exit(0) gracefully if SESSION_STRING missing

DEPLOYMENT:
- Platform: Railway
- Entry: uvicorn backend.api.api_server:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port $PORT
- Background threads: master_scheduler.py + telegram_listener.py
- Volume: mounted at data directory

